      "review_summary": "The PR threads optional `toolCallId` through WebChat stream segment types and adjusts chat item sorting so a matching live tool card cannot render before the assistant stream segment that introduced it.\n\nPR surface: Source +41, Tests +123. Total +164 across 6 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. Current main commits stream segments with local timestamps and matching tool IDs, then sorts visible chat items by raw timestamp only, so an older tool-event timestamp can render ahead of the stream text that caused it.",
